'''Muti waka Hlatshwayo''' i muti lowu vulavulaka Xichangana na Xizulu. 

==Matimu ya Muti== 

== Xithopo xa muti ==
<blockquote>
''Matlhavana... (Mukwana)''<BR>
''Mukwana... (matlhavana)''<BR>
''Hlatshwayo va ka Mukwana wa ku tlhava wu tlhela wu tsema matlhelo hinkwawo,''<BR> 
''va ka Mukwana wa xinyayi va ka Gama ra nsele,''<BR>
''va ku cangayila va ka swingelengele,''<BR>
''va ka swikarhati leswi kulu va ku humula hi vusiku ku etlela,''<BR>
''va ka Nghwanya Mathambo ka Huweni''<BR>
</blockquote>

Lexi hi xona xi thopo lexi tivekaka xa muti lowu. Kuni ku hambana-nyana eka swi mutana swa ka Hlatshwayo loko swiri karhi swi thopa xivongo lexi.

== Rhavi e ka swiyenge swa rixaka ra machangana ==
Hi ku ya hi [[Henri-Alexandre Junod|Henri Junod]] va ka Hlatshwayo, va hlayiwa eka rhavi ra '''Va Djonga''' e ka rixaka ra machangana.<ref>Henry Junod - Life of a South African Tribe - Vol 1, Pages 16 - 19</ref>

